MASU+ Institutional v4.5
Overview
MASU+ Institutional v4.5+ is the refined, open-source version of our classic trend-following strategy. It is designed for traders who want a robust, "set-and-forget" algorithmic assistant that combines Institutional Moving Average Ribbons with Smart Money Concepts (SMC).

Unlike the complex v7 execution engine (Invite-Only), this v4.5+ version focuses on pure Trend Alignment & Structural Clarity. It is cleaner, faster, and visually optimized for daily market analysis.

Key Features in v4 Final
1. Institutional MA Ribbon Engine
Logic: Instead of complex kernels, v4.5+ uses a classic 8-EMA Ribbon.
Signal: Buying pressure is confirmed only when the ribbon fully aligns (Green Expansion). Selling pressure is confirmed on Red Expansion.
Why it works: It filters out 90% of sideways chop, keeping you out of bad trades during low-volume hours.

2. Smart Money Structure (SMC)
Auto-BOS: Automatically detects Break of Structure to confirm trend validity.
Liquidity Sweeps: Marks "Liquidity Grabs" (LIQ X) where price traps retail traders.
Demand & Supply Zones: Dynamically plots unfilled order blocks (Blue/Orange boxes) that act as magnets for price.

3. Volatility & Order Flow
Volume Pressure: Analyzes buying vs. selling volume within each candle.
Regime Detection: Filters trades based on ADX and BB Width (Trending vs. Ranging).

4. Institutional Dashboard

Live Scanner: A comprehensive panel showing Trend Status (15m, 1H, 4H), Risk/Reward metrics, and active signals in real-time.
Strategy Logic (How it Trades)
This strategy executes a trade only when a High-Confluence Setup occurs:
Trend: 15m, 1H, and 4H trends must align.
Structure: Price must break structure (BOS) or bounce from a Demand Zone.
Volume: Order Flow must confirm the move (Green Volume Pressure).

Exit Logic:

Take Profit: Fixed 3.0x ATR target.
Stop Loss: Fixed 2.0x ATR protection.
Trailing Stop: Activates to lock in profits during strong trends.

⚠️ v4.5+ vs. v7 (Comparison)
v4.5+ (This Script):
✅ Free & Open Source
✅ Classic MA Ribbon Logic
✅ Standard Risk Management (Fixed SL/TP)
❌ No Equity Guard (Account Protection)
❌ No BOS-Confirmed Execution (Instant Entry)
❌ No Neural Network (AI)

v7 (Invite-Only):

🚀 Nadaraya-Watson Kernel (Adaptive)
🚀 ELM Neural Network (AI Filter)
🚀 BOS-Confirmed Entries (Scalping Module)
🚀 Equity Guard (Drawdown Protection)
🚀 Cost-Aware Filtering (Spread Protection)

Recommended Settings
Timeframe: 1Н
Assets: XAUUSD, EURUSD, BTCUSD, US30.
Risk: Defaults to Kelly Criterion sizing, but you can adjust to Fixed % in settings.
Clean code. Clear signals. Institutional logic.
